rows.name:
Hey, guys! Check out this Deviled
Baguette recipe I picked up!

rows.label: tlk70000060_01_msg0002
rows.name:
The more recipes you get ahold of,
the better your cooking repertoire
will be!

rows.label: tlk70000060_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Sometimes people'll give you them,
or you might get a sudden brainwave!
It's happened to me, anyway!

rows.label: tlk70000060_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Also, it can be a ton of fun collecting
recipes, but don't forget to actually try
some out. Trust me, you'll love it!
